com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger

Class FileLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger.AbstractLogger
      • com.lsc.ctesterfx.logger.FileLogger

  • public class FileLogger
extends AbstractLogger
    Class that logs the results in a file. Every test controller will contain an instance of this class. The TestController must ensure that the logger is set up before the test starts.
    Author:
    dma@logossmartcard.com
